# Native plugin binaries (.dylib / .dll / .so) ARE tracked — but via Git
# LFS pointing at forgejo.kbve.com/KBVE/rareicon. See .gitattributes +
# .lfsconfig. Removing the historical ignore lines so LFS pointer files
# get committed; without that, git silently skips the binaries entirely.

